    "rationale": "Despite all seven assessed credibility factors achieving levels below their required levels and six factors remaining unassessed, the assessment team accepted the package on the basis of the consolidated multi-study synthesis evidence (ValidationSynthesisResult node) which was treated as an established foundational evidentiary basis. The synthesis was considered self-evidently foundational given its extensive literature citations. Monte Carlo UQ results confirm the 95th-percentile hemolysis index remains below the clinical threshold across all operating points, providing sufficient risk-based justification for conditional acceptance pending resolution of the discretization and model form gaps in the next submission cycle.",
